cs.CR, cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.SE 

This paper discusses the security of IoT devices and their communications in edge networks, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and computer networks (cs.NI). The proposed system, IoT-Keeper, uses anomaly detection techniques, which can be categorized under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and system and control (cs.SY). The paper also discusses the challenges of securing IoT devices due to insecure product development practices, which can be categorized under software engineering (cs.SE).
